Our agent is implemented using java programming. In future,  we are planning to use mobile agents for resource monitoring for proper resource utilization. Eucalyptus was used to  create virtual machines with a centos image customized with java and tomcat server. On top of each VM, CPU  intensive application and memory intensive application such factorial calculation and finding paths in a graph were  considered to test the performances of virtual machines.
